A: The roomowner can start the PK competition between everyone through the scoreboard in the room, and determine the winner within a period of time through the score of each user; \nRoomowner can reset the scoring by ending the current round to start a new round;

Q: What does it mean to end this round?

Q: What is the time limit?

Q: How to edit or close the scoreboard?
A: After the scoreboard is turned on, the original scoreboard button will change to Close & Edit. After clicking the button, you can edit the scoreboard duration or close the scoreboard;
Q: Why is Winner empty in the historical record?
